Get latest data

Source: vignettes/latest_data.Rmd
latest_data.Rmd

This vignette is meant for those who want to get the latest data from the Washington Post Github repo.

library(wapoposh)

Usage

Get latest data (if newer version is available)

latest <- latest_data()
#> [1] "No update available. Returning existing package dataset."
tail(latest, 4)
